description:
Stay Close, was widely heralded for its solid songwriting, its musical ingenuity and for the unique quality of Thibodeau&#039;s crooning. His soprano register is exceptionally high for a male and even pre-pubescent sounding. Death Vessel has toured with Iron & Wine, Low, Jose Gonzalez, and The Books, among others.
